                        <blockquote class="mt-3">
                            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                                "Thesis stress had me lying awake until 4 AM every night. Lulla's program was so much better than the sleep meds my doctor prescribed. I actually learned skills that last!"
